Photo of the jalal Lahar Skilkhor

Jalal was born in kharkoo Lahar in 03-04-1991.he has gotten primary education in kharkoo Lahar.and after he has gone to Daghoni for middle and high education.then jalal went to khaplu after Sakardu for graduation B.A education.just after it jalal enrollment in police department.he spent five years in Gilgit.snd two years in khaplu.in kharkoo Lahar 20 men are police. Well talented police in Baltistan. Jalal has two doughters and only son.
